{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1809449, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "第二个，应该", "timestamp": 1623129247, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809469, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "应试教育摧毁不了灵气，包括学科竞赛的大部分高考外升学手段才会摧毁公平", "timestamp": 1623129439, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809473, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你清大多数人都是受过应试教育“折磨”的，你觉得你的同学中表现出不可逆的精神损伤的人多吗", "timestamp": 1623129497, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "应试的话语文阅卷多半按北京标准吧，或者说是西城海淀标准吧，朝阳区优秀范文都是反面教材，那你想想河北得多惨", "timestamp": 1623129764, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809488, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在数学系不是有yau班么", "timestamp": 1623129809, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809490, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从前也有各种预科，保送", "timestamp": 1623129850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809509, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": 1809473, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 清华还好。别的学校我感觉还是有几个的", "timestamp": 1623130205, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809516, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得高考最大问题是浪费时间，高中那点东西放到大学一年不到就能学完，还搞三年，还拼死拼活的，没那个必要。", "timestamp": 1623130291, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1809549, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 355484, "reply_to": 1809469, "tag": null, "text": "Re B